label: Billingsgate Roman House & Baths (Museum)
column5: Beneath London's Square Mile lies a well-preserved Roman history that has withstood centuries of change. The Billingsgate Roman House and Baths
column7: offer a fascinating glimpse into Roman London

label: Bozioru Cave Dwellings
column5: The mystical cave complex in Buzau County
column7: spans over 5 square kilometers and includes ancient caves
column9: and hermitages that date back to the Bronze Age. Notable sites include a stone church from 1274 and Dionysius the Spinner Cave
column10: where a monk lived in solitude
column11: with some caves even containing frescoes and symbols carved into the walls.
